Hiptest publisher samples with Cucumber/Java

In this repository you'll find tests generated in Cucumber/Java format from Hiptest, using Hiptest publisher.

The goals are:

to show how tests are exported in Cucumber/Java.
to check exports work out of the box
Update tests

To update the tests:

"hiptest-publisher -c cucumber-java-ci.conf --only=features,step_definitions"

Run tests

To build the project and run the tests, use the following command:

mvn test

The test report is generated in target/cuke-results-junit.xml